Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.54,0:01:36.21,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Ladies and gentlemen,\ngood evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.11,0:01:38.84,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Everything lies in ruin.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.05,0:01:45.28,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What was once believed to be solid ground\nhas opened up and swallowed everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.36,0:01:50.95,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The young soul wanders aimlessly,\nbetrayed by everything he had believed in.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.73,0:01:57.03,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But what he clutches at\nin the end is...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.14,0:02:06.14,count alt,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(352,352)}Act 17:\NThe Confession
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.21,0:02:41.84,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Someone taught me the\nmeaning of the word hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.55,0:02:45.84,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Count, that someone\nwas you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.46,0:03:01.29,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Wait for me, Albert!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.97,0:03:08.30,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Mademoiselle.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.91,0:03:11.77,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,A letter has arrived\nfor you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.21,0:03:13.57,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.76,0:03:29.82,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Why aren't you\nsaying anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.56,0:03:36.43,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Why aren't you\nanswering me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.87,0:03:42.93,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,My words now fall\non deaf ears.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.24,0:03:46.73,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Is... Is that what you're\ntrying to say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.84,0:03:53.61,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,There is no such thing as coincidence.\NI believe that is what I told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.95,0:03:58.15,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,As I recall, it is the very\nfirst thing I told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.12,0:04:01.85,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Everything that happens\ndoes so out of necessity.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.96,0:04:03.62,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What are you trying\nto say?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.59,0:04:09.55,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me, if Haidee were not a living witness\nto your father's true identity,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.10,0:04:14.20,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...what value would there\nbe in keeping her with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.17,0:04:19.87,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me, if you were not\NMondego's son,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.21,0:04:24.81,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...why would it have been necessary\nfor me to meet you on Luna?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.38,0:04:27.64,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.52,0:04:33.32,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,From the very beginning,\nyou were using me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.56,0:04:37.72,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I met you under the\npretense of coincidence,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.83,0:04:43.73,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...and took advantage of this so-called\N"friendship" that you have such faith in.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.07,0:04:45.47,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That is what\NI am saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.04,0:04:49.03,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I even used props\nsuch as that watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.88,0:04:55.14,count alt,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.05,0:04:59.61,count alt,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,From the very beginning,\nyou were using me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.95,0:05:00.64,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You're lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.75,0:05:02.34,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You're lying! You're lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.12,0:05:06.75,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe that everything has been\na setup since the very beginning!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.99,0:05:07.96,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.56,0:05:14.05,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, haven't you always\nhelped me, Count?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.80,0:05:17.79,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Haven't you always been\nlooking out for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.60,0:05:23.97,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I don't believe that all the time\nwe spent together was a lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.61,0:05:25.90,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Not one bit!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.53,0:05:50.00,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You poor, foolish boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.33,0:05:55.20,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You still wish to remain immersed\Nin those naive delusions of yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.40,0:05:57.43,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Is that what you\nare trying to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.41,0:06:03.34,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I deliberately brought you with me\non that pleasure cruise that day,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.68,0:06:07.31,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...knowing full well that Haidee was about to\ndisclose the truth at the National Assembly?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.50,0:06:28.87,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I must thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.51,0:06:33.70,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You have been most useful to me\nin the time we have known one another.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.54,0:06:40.31,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You have my gratitude.\NFrom the bottom of my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.08,0:07:12.31,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I challenge you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.65,0:07:15.01,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,My, how old-fashioned.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.19,0:07:19.68,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The son of a soldier must act\nin accordance with tradition?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.79,0:07:22.02,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Is that it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.56,0:07:24.99,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The time will be tomorrow morning\nat five.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.33,0:07:26.79,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,In the forest of Boulogne.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.60,0:07:28.76,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Weapons?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.16,0:07:31.00,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Armor and bare steel!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.43,0:07:32.59,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.17,0:07:36.43,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Bertuccio.\NYou are my witness.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.74,0:07:39.54,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Did you see the whole challenge\nfrom beginning to end?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.74,0:07:41.27,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes, Excellency!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.41,0:07:48.08,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Albert!\NI accept your challenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.75,0:07:53.81,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, we will meet\nat five tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.03,0:08:34.29,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It will serve to freeze the memory\nof this day, this hour, in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.63,0:08:37.16,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,A memory which belongs\nto us alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.62,0:09:01.18,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I must go see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.90,0:09:19.86,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Count, is there nothing I can do to stop\nthis duel between you and Albert?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.31,0:09:26.37,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You told me\nthat I am free.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.22,0:09:32.15,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That is what allowed me to live to\nthis day without taking my own life.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.36,0:09:38.29,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But if you... If you were\nto perish,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.50,0:09:42.33,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...I would not be able\nto go on living, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.97,0:09:50.44,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Gankutsuou...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.97,0:09:53.94,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Wait... Not yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.51,0:09:59.47,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It is not yet time!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.44,0:10:24.60,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Franz?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.61,0:10:27.84,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Albert!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.56,0:10:44.65,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Franz...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.83,0:10:48.49,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You've always\nlooked out for me,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.93,0:10:54.39,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...but I'd always plunge ahead with what\NI was doing, ignoring your advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.64,0:10:58.00,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry...\NI'm so sorry, Franz.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.48,0:11:03.81,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.28,0:11:06.87,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.42,0:11:10.94,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, wipe the snot\nfrom your nose.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.42,0:11:12.79,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Get off my back!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.39,0:11:19.85,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You total idiot! You played\nstraight into his hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.30,0:11:22.86,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You've got to call off this duel\nright now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.97,0:11:24.33,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Cut it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.63,0:11:27.53,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You'll act as\nmy second, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.37,0:11:32.24,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I don't blame you\nfor being angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.37,0:11:36.64,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But this is one thing that I have\nto see through, no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.58,0:11:39.55,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to me,\nand listen good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.65,0:11:42.58,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The Count has been planning\nto kill you all along.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.85,0:11:45.95,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying that you don't care if you end\nup getting killed in the name of his revenge?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.05,0:11:47.04,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Franz.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.22,0:11:52.28,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That bastard deceived me\nand used dirty tricks to lure me in.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.90,0:11:55.19,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,He used the most despicable means\nimaginable to toy with me...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.33,0:11:57.49,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...and turn my life\nupside-down.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.77,0:12:00.70,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And I can't... I can't let him\nget away with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.51,0:12:10.27,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Even if the Count used to be\nyour mother's fiancé?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.45,0:12:14.75,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Your father was so in love\nwith your mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.12,0:12:18.45,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...that 25 years ago, he framed the Count\Nfor a crime he didn't commit...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.55,0:12:21.82,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...and took his fiancée\naway from him by force.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.40,0:12:29.99,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Edmond Dantes?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.51,0:12:46.78,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Mondego's wife is here\nto see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.75,0:12:49.88,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Edmond!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.79,0:12:53.22,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No, Count...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.39,0:12:58.59,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You are really Edmond Dantes,\naren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.96,0:13:03.66,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,How I've missed you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.60,0:13:11.23,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,These past 25 years, I haven't\nforgotten you for an instant.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.41,0:13:16.64,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I know that you can never\nforgive what I've done.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.68,0:13:27.58,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But... But even if only once, I wish I could\nspeak with you as Edmond!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.50,0:13:43.70,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Edmond... is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.44,0:13:49.27,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This body retains only his\nshape and appearance.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.61,0:13:54.57,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,There is no longer anything\nof Edmond himself left within it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.75,0:13:55.65,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.22,0:14:00.42,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No, that isn't possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.82,0:14:09.99,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If that were so, why have I had the feeling ever\nsince the day we met that you are Edmond?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.78,0:14:28.01,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You refuse to be disturbed\nby the coldness of my hand...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.85,0:14:32.15,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You leave me\nno choice, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.83,0:14:46.10,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I will show you proof that Edmond,\nthe man you once loved, is now dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.54,0:14:58.00,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I will await you at five tomorrow morning\nin the forest of Boulogne.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.83,0:15:19.53,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's already too late\nfor that, Franz.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.60,0:15:22.54,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's too late\nto do anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.01,0:15:26.81,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever happened between the Count\nand our fathers in the past,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.18,0:15:29.58,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...I don't care about\nany of that anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.45,0:15:34.38,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I can't take back what happened\nbetween the Count and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.75,0:15:39.98,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If he hates me that much, he should\njust kill me and be done with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.69,0:15:41.71,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.82,0:15:45.62,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,He played games with\nmy feelings!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.43,0:15:48.76,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Albert! Don't do it!\NDon't go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.00,0:15:50.09,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.63,0:15:51.86,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Albert!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.90,0:15:56.63,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Please, come back...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.15,0:16:14.68,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You're still going to go see him,\neven knowing who he is?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.93,0:17:26.59,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.70,0:17:28.89,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Franz! You're back!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.00,0:17:33.19,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.34,0:17:36.60,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Is Albert here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.71,0:17:40.61,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... No, he was with me\nuntil a while ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.64,0:17:43.27,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,He said that he had something\nto take care of.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.35,0:17:45.78,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, he did?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.78,0:17:50.84,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Still, I'm glad to see you. I haven't been\nable to reach you since that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.19,0:17:53.28,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for worrying you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.42,0:17:56.88,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly! I was worried\nsick about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.49,0:18:00.86,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You timed your\narrival perfectly, Franz.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.24,0:18:11.57,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Franz, don't you remember?\NTomorrow is Albert's birthday!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.04,0:18:17.31,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, exactly! That's why!\NThat's why I came to see you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.65,0:18:19.44,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, get your\nact together...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.55,0:18:23.42,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, about that...\NI wrote a song for Albert!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.79,0:18:25.51,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's not finished yet,\nthough.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.58,0:18:49.54,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.74,0:18:51.84,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it's nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.38,0:18:55.68,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's romantic.\NNot like you at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.92,0:18:58.18,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What's that supposed to mean?!\NDon't be rude!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.03,0:19:17.16,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That settles it! Tomorrow, you, Albert and I\nwill have a party at our usual cafe!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.01,0:19:20.20,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.78,0:19:24.23,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Just say that a friend of yours is having\na recital or something, and sneak out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.35,0:19:25.68,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It'll all work out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.65,0:19:29.34,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.65,0:19:32.35,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So anyway, do you think you\ncould do me a little favor?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.59,0:19:33.55,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,As in?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.76,0:19:37.21,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I wrote a message in\na birthday card for him,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.73,0:19:43.46,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...but I think we're too old for that kind of thing,\nso I feel awkward giving it to him in person.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.57,0:19:47.00,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot, who cares how old you are?\NYou're just giving him a card.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.27,0:19:52.04,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, give it to Albert\nafter I leave tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.54,0:19:53.97,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Please?\NI'm begging you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.11,0:19:59.60,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It must be a surprise.\NSure, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.08,0:20:03.52,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I think I'll keep working\non that song for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.29,0:20:08.59,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't work too hard.\NSee you tomorrow at 3 PM, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.92,0:20:10.29,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,At our usual cafe.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.63,0:20:16.93,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for coming by\nto visit me today.
